# Please do not shoot the programmer. He is doing his best

## My Open Source Projects
* [**wm-html-include.js**](http://al-scvorets.github.io/wm-html-include.js/) -- a small script to include external HTML page(s) into comprising HTML page
* [**wm-yom-parse.js**](http://al-scvorets.github.io/wm-yom-parse.js/) -- converts the data from the mysterious language Yom into javascript object
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
